                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d01">
                      Decorative designs: <locus target="#4r #22r #49r #62r #74v #100v #118r #119r"/> (ornate ḥaräg);
                      <locus target="#14r #27v #37r #56v #74r #85v #88v #94r #112v"/> (lines of alternating red and black dots</decoNote>
